    <!-- Home: theme description -->
    <string name="home_theme_description">More than a name, "Root Further" is the spirit every Sun* aspires to: always looking deeper in every context and never ceasing to create, expanding oneself to overcome self-imposed limits. Borrowing the metaphor of color theory, from just three primaries — red, yellow, and blue — each individual\'s creativity can produce nearly limitless new shades, every hue representing breakthrough and boundless creation.</string>

